# Geralds House
![gerald](data:image/jpeg;base64,)
### Summary

We have created an application for you constuction requiring 2X4's, It covers the width and length of a house and returns the number of studs required to frame the walls inside the 4x4 beam.

## Please read this first
* Another item
* Unordered sub-list



Example :
---


node dist/index.js -w 8 -l 8
